{
  "stem": "512.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And as we arrived in Auschwitz-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] excuse me-- [CRYING] [DRINKS] after several days-- I don't know, maybe five days-- we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we saw that there were a lot of Nazis by the, by the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And also, the prison uniforms, those were the Jewish boys, the Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we got out, they announced it, a loudspeaker, nobody was to take anything out from the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And everything, everything yet will get to your destination.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And mothers and the children on one side, and younger men on the other side, and young, healthy-looking men, women on one side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were all with my mother, with all the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No, but then Jewish, Jewish fellows that were working there came over to me and grabbed me by the arm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, you go in that group, and pinch your cheeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess I was-- we were extremely already undernourished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my sister followed me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother only shouted, take care.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING] Sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] And that was the last goodbye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] My mother and the four children with her friend with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father went separately with the young, with the men, with the working men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] they said they're going to take the mothers and the children on trucks, and we will march.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We will walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mengele was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the first time we saw Mengele, and he was the one that was going through and left, right, left, right.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So they finally rounded us up, the working ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
